    public static class ForgeGuiFactory.ForgeConfigGui.ChunkLoaderEntry
extends GuiConfigEntries.CategoryEntry
    This custom list entry provides the Forge Chunk Manager Config entry on the Minecraft Forge Configuration screen. It extends the base Category entry class and defines the IConfigElement objects that will be used to build the child screen.
